title: The League Cup Show Quarter Final Highlights 18.12.2013 EPL
description:
The League Cup Show Quarter Final Highlights - 18.12.2013

Duration: 49 minutes

The Capital One Cup reaches the quarter-final stage and we've extended highlights from all four ties. 

Our featured match comes from White Hart Lane as Spurs meet West Ham in a London derby. And there is the best of the action from Stoke's tie against Manchester United, Leicester's match with Manchester City and Sunderland's head to head with Chelsea. 

All the drama brought to you by Manish Bhasin
